🏗 Section 4: Principles of Enterprise Delivery

Role & Position in the Manual
	•	This is the philosophical foundation of the manual. While other sections teach “how to do,” this one helps the reader understand why we do it this way.
	•	It defines the guardrail logic — principles that should never be violated even if you adapt rituals.
	•	It ensures alignment: whenever someone questions a process later, you can refer back to these principles as the source of legitimacy.

⸻

🎯 Promise of the Content (What This Section Delivers)

By the end of Section 4, the reader will:
	•	Understand a coherent set of guiding principles that unify all the tactical practices in the manual.
	•	Be able to judge new situations by measuring them against these principles (i.e. a candidate tactic either aligns or conflicts).
	•	Gain clarity on the boundary between discipline and dogma — what is mandatory, what is optional.
	•	Build confidence in invoking principles during conflict (“We can’t skip test coverage because it violates our quality principle”).
	•	Internalize a mindset shift: from “we have to follow process” to “we choose to follow principles for protection and predictability.”

